title: Voting for this game launch
body:
A ready-to-launch mobile online private server game for FUN. 
Free to play and earn FREE NFTs in events. 
NFTs is the prize, you can hold or trade on marketplaces.NFTs are collection characters in the game. Rare and beautifully!
No need to waste your money on delayed game projects anymore!
Only need to stake your assets(BNB, USDT, etc...) at Flintstone Finance to harvest STONE token, and spend STONE token in-game. 
YOUR MONEY IS ALWAYS SAFE!!
The demo is here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CkKJVzZJO10
